    Revision:
      ccze--0.1--patch-56

    * src/ccze-plugin.c (_ccze_plugin_load_set): New function.
      (ccze_plugin_load_all): Utilise _ccze_plugin_load_set() to load
      plugins from under ~/.ccze/ and PLUGIN_LIBPATH.

    modified files:
     ChangeLog src/ccze-plugin.c


