    Revision:
      ccze--0.1--patch-30

    * src/ccze-wordcolor.c (ccze_wordcolor_process): Compare the
      lower-cased word with all those regexps, and in case of
      good/badwords, only colour the word if the badword matches the
      beginning of the word.

