    * src/ccze-wordcolor.c (words_error): Added `alarm'.
      (ccze_wordcolor_setup): Do not place any requirement on the length
      of reg_size, so we can catch `0.21Kbyte/sec' too.

    modified files:
     ChangeLog src/ccze-wordcolor.c


